oded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3524:\"<p><img src=\"http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_social_network_tabs.png\" alt=\"Social Network Tabs\" class=\"img-border\" /></p>\n<p>Version 1.6 of <a href=\"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/\" class=\"external underline\">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a> and <a href=\"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/\" class=\"external underline\">WordPress Social Network Tabs</a> now includes the Instagram API, bringing the total number of supported networks to 17 with 49 feed options!</p>\n<h3>Instagram Tab Feed Options</h3>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/instagram_api_feed_tab.jpg\" alt=\"Instagram Feed Tab\" class=\"img-right hide-excerpt\" /></p>\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\n<li>Show an Instagram user feed</li>\n<li>Search Instagram tags</li>\n<li>Show an Instagram Location ID feed</li>\n<li>Search by latitude/longitude + distance</li>\n<li>Show post likes with user thumbnail avatar</li>\n<li>Show latest comments</li>\n<li>Select image size &#8211; 306 px, 150 px or 612 px</li>\n</ul>\n<p>In addition to the Instagram update the plugin now includes the ability to display twitter search feeds and options to disable both retweets and twitter replies.</p>\n<h3>View The Plugin Demos</h3>\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\n<li><a href=\"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-media-tabs-plugin/\" class=\"underline\">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/premium-wordpress-plugins/premium-wordpress-plugin-social-network-tabs/\" class=\"underline\">Social Network Tabs for WordPress</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Purchase From Codecanyon</h3>\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\n<li><a href=\"http://codecanyon.net/item/jquery-social-media-tabs/1932796?ref=designchemical\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external underline\">jQuery Social Media Tabs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://codecanyon.net/item/social-network-tabs-for-wordpress/1982987?ref=designchemical\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external underline\">Social Network Tabs for WordPress</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?a=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:-BTjWOF_DHI\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/DesignChemical?i=sr4nKXO7Jj4:rXf3IIEAvAk:-BTjWOF_DHI\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/DesignChemical/~4/sr4nKXO7Jj4\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:132:\"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/wordpress-plugins/instagram-added-to-jquery-wordpress