\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:682:\"<p><img src=\"http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/jquery_social_stream.jpg\" alt=\"jQuery Social Stream\" class=\"img-border\" /></p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into a single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Includes 13 social networks with a total of 24 different feed options.</p>\n<p>Using only jQuery, the social stream plugin can be used for ANY website &#8230; including WordPress &#8230; no PHP required!</p>\n<p>View jQuery Social Stream Plugin Demo  &#8230; <a href=\"http://www.designchemical.com/blog/index.php/jquery-plugins/new-premium-jquery-plugin-jquery-social-stream/\" class=\"read_more\">more</a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Admin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4945:\"<p><img src=\"http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/jquery_social_stream.jpg\" alt=\"jQuery Social Stream\" class=\"img-border\" /></p>\n<p>Combine all of your social network interactions into a single network stream or create a single feed for multiple social network profiles. Includes 13 social networks with a total of 24 different feed options.</p>\n<p>Using only jQuery, the social stream plugin can be used for ANY website &#8230; including WordPress &#8230; no PHP required!</p>\n<p><a href=\"/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/\" class=\"external underline\">View jQuery Social Stream Plugin Demo Site</a></p>\n<h3>Plugin Supports 13 Social Networks</h3>\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\n<li>Twitter &#8211; Latest Tweets</li>\n<li>Facebook &#8211; Page Latest Wall Posts</li>\n<li>Google +1 &#8211; Latest +1 Posts</li>\n<li>RSS Feed &#8211; Latest Posts</li>\n<li>Delicious &#8211; Latest Likes</li>\n<li>Stumbleupon &#8211; Favorites or Reviews</li>\n<li>Pinterest &#8211; Latest Pins</li>\n<li>Dribbble &#8211; Latest Shots or Likes</li>\n<li>Youtube &#8211; Latest Uploads or Favorites</li>\n<li>Vimeo &#8211; Likes, Videos, Appeared In, Albums, Channels or Groups</li>\n<li>Flickr &#8211; Latest Uploads</li>\n<li>last.fm &#8211; Loved Tracks, Recent Tracks or Reply Tracker</li>\n<li>Deviantart &#8211; Latest Deviations</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Social Stream Display Options</h3>\n<p>Display using rotating feed list or a filterable jQuery Isotope powered Social Network Wall!</p>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<p><strong>Includes 2 sample skins for the rotating list:</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/dcsns_feed.png\" alt=\"jQuery Social Stream Feed\" class=\"img-border\" /></div>\n<div style=\"float: right;\">\n<p><strong>Pinterest style Social Network Wall:</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www.designchemical.com/media/images/dcsns_wall.png\" alt=\"jQuery Social Stream Network Wall\" class=\"img-border\" /></div>\n<p class=\"clear\">Options include setting the stream to display items by date based on total number of days or number of latest feed items from each network.</p>\n<h3>jQuery Social Media Tabs Plugin Demos</h3>\n<p>Check out the <a href=\"/blog/index.php/premium-jquery-plugins/jquery-social-stream-plugin/\" class=\"underline\">plugin home page</a> for more details or view the social stream demos:</p>\n<div class=\"banner-horizontal float-right\">\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\ngoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7740611438413740\";\n/* Link Mid Content */\ngoogle_ad_slot = \"2373698085\";\ngoogle_ad_width = 200;\ngoogle_ad_height = 90;\n//-->\n</script><br />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"content-list\">\n<li><a href=\